      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Insurance Claim Management System",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Insurance Claim Management System",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Jj5SqgUEeZZ_L5fjrVQFY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4373.084980584117,
      "y": -1680.750183658438,
      "width": 306.0718994140625,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0W",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2124725535,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 1452708095,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Project Objective",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Project Objective",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8-QAKwa4eDcTzzmF6BvYZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4637.144810296031,
      "y": -1613.250183658438,
      "width": 698.1595458984375,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0X",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 954755153,
      "version": 5,
      "versionNonce": 1888895601,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The objective of this project is to\nsimplify and automate the insurance\nbeneficiary payout process.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The objective of this project is to simplify and automate the insurance beneficiary payout process.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DM8RpF0ZoiFPe-Vp6tAHV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4687.714726067516,
      "y": -1555.750183658438,
      "width": 799.2993774414062,
      "height": 405,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0Y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1986904383,
      "version": 5,
      "versionNonce": 1018829087,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When a policyholder passes away, the\ninsurance company must verify the\nbeneficiary's claim before releasing the\ninsurance amount. In a traditional process,\nemployees perform these tasks manually by\nchecking documents, sending emails for\napprovals, maintaining spreadsheets, and\ntracking the status through phone calls or\npaperwork.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When a policyholder passes away, the insurance company must verify the beneficiary's claim before releasing the insurance amount. In a traditional process, employees perform these tasks manually by checking documents, sending emails for approvals, maintaining spreadsheets, and tracking the status through phone calls or paperwork.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "O2XmOrk3gViCP2wcJzQy3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4678.044712639781,
      "y": -1345.750183658438,
      "width": 1403.9276123046875,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0Z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1094268465,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 375835729,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "This manual process is time-consuming, prone to errors, and difficult to monitor.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "This manual process is time-consuming, prone to errors, and difficult to monitor.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "JmSmF7lAteXjgT8Cb7cjb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4687.154789544078,
      "y": -1303.250183658438,
      "width": 798.1795043945312,
      "height": 360,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1925267807,
      "version": 5,
      "versionNonce": 24616255,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "To solve this problem, I developed the\nInsurance Claim Management System, which\nautomates the entire beneficiary payout\nprocess. The application ensures that every\nclaim is routed to the correct person,\napprovals are taken according to business\nrules, and the claim is completed efficiently\nwith complete traceability.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "To solve this problem, I developed the Insurance Claim Management System, which automates the entire beneficiary payout process. The application ensures that every claim is routed to the correct person, approvals are taken according to business rules, and the claim is completed efficiently with complete traceability.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "kr698ET6lTdRytzfLkD_0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4300.395016289684,
      "y": -1130.750183658438,
      "width": 44.387969970703125,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0b",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 99960849,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 692787761,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "---",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "---",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QdJplcmsmP4hMYZhi_Zso",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4452.704899407359,
      "y": -1060.750183658438,
      "width": 592.7037963867188,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0c",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1961868671,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 942644575,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Why was this application created?",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Why was this application created?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VFthk4B02wfsYpM35MpUI",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4668.88473949525,
      "y": -993.2501836584379,
      "width": 761.639404296875,
      "height": 135,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0d",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1628708337,
      "version": 5,
      "versionNonce": 1512746001,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Imagine an insurance company receives\nhundreds of death claim requests every\nday.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Imagine an insurance company receives hundreds of death claim requests every day.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6liSIWRhfG1LtjL__AWmJ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4438.034947014781,
      "y": -895.7501836584379,
      "width": 539.8917846679688,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0e",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 3782047,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 875731327,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Without an automated system:",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Without an automated system:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KToS4-MWp-i2mRr1VIoYi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4489.274876214,
      "y": -825.7501836584379,
      "width": 724.3556518554688,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0f",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 27080657,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 1358758385,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Employees manually verify policy details.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Employees manually verify policy details.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "OBFVoFbNS57yS_HXDllfv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -4650.614750481578,
      "y": -790.7501836584379,
      "width": 1305.1795654296875,
      "height": 45,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0g",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1540336063,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 180425119,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782707405649,
